; Regression test for issue #723: -S t doesn't sort timelog entries correctly (BZ#723)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/723
;
; When sorting timelog entries by total (-S t), entries with equal durations
; are not correctly sorted by date. Here 03/03 (2.00h) appears before 03/02 (2.00h)
; instead of the chronologically correct order.

i 2013/03/03 10:00:00 Work
o 2013/03/03 12:00:00
i 2013/03/01 09:00:00 Work
o 2013/03/01 10:30:00
i 2013/03/02 14:00:00 Work
o 2013/03/02 16:00:00

test reg -S t
13-Mar-01                       Work                          1.50h        1.50h
13-Mar-03                       Work                          2.00h        3.50h
13-Mar-02                       Work                          2.00h        5.50h
end test
